Below are structured UAT / SIT test cases to be shared with the GC team for validation.
These are aligned with the latest decisions (non-mandatory fields, default values, master-driven fields, and portal sync requirements).

📘 Test Case Document

Objective:
To validate policy generation and successful synchronization with GC portal as per agreed data dictionary and default handling rules.

